{"tid":1593300,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對準政權 五大訴求 缺一不可","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T08:06:15.000Z","uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3a871a7096fa38cc9b10efcd3508b2cf3056ead","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:13:19.000Z","msg":"停一停 諗一諗 成日又要搞黨鐵 搞美心 個頭又走去做神探 再轉個頭仲變身埋問米婆 <br />\n<br />\n我地最初出黎既目的係咩？ <br />\n<br />\n係對政策既不信任 係對政制既不滿 係對政府既不公不義作公民抗命呀 <br />\n<br />\n我地既目標 永遠都係 五大訴求 <br />\n<br />\n港鐵跪左 香港唔會變 美心跪左 香港都係唔會變 警察呢一刻跪左 過二三年 一樣係咁 只有當整個政制既改革得到實行 有一個完善既機制互相監測制衡 自係香港真正既出路 <br />\n<br />\n我知大家會火遮眼 我都會 但我地 輸唔起<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"d4177efb1d5c0284729eae015193abae68420c2e","tid":1593300,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"be664ed2545ebadf440039bdba69e20e5ad140d7","tid":1593300,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"39ce95ae191f2965fed34d9cad84530521ada73c","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:16:08.000Z","msg":"更多人睇到"},{"pid":"08a177f24eb15ef26b5e548bf1dd88139c2b7f64","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:17:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65bd80aff2