g>Twitter戰線<br />\n每晚10點上Twitter/Reddit upload文宣</strong><br />\n宣傳ChiNazi 同記得集中hashtag<br />\n#929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism<br />\n#ChiNazi"},{"pid":"20f9b0a7690b0437e5bad41c1e7e9db7295fca87","tid":1593300,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:35:06.000Z","msg":"對準政權"},{"pid":"1102a0da054ce48dcbe4cd57f0614f86428aa63d","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04eba586e99ebfa8d47a7deacd64f9d71ad56f39","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d9709713daa8aede016b8713c64d507853618a2","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa27fd59257bc160d1d5cc222bd531c20ca4aec6","tid":1593300,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"sorry ,幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[文宣工作]入黎揀個宣傳方法去做！重現69吹大雞！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593328\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593328</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>1.網絡宣傳+airdrop</strong></span><br />\n最易，亦都有好多巴絲做緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />辛苦哂<br />\n大家可以幫手post 去 fb,ig,twitter, <span style=\"color: red;\">仲有香討等各大論壇！</span>講真上得連登大部分都了解黎緊有咩活動，但仲有一大班人玩開其他論壇， 我建議可以用洗連登式洗各論壇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>2.各區連儂牆+各戶大廈𨋢口，洗樓</strong></span><br />\n連儂牆基本啦，唔洗多講，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家可以痴文宣係自己大廈𨋢口度，咁啲人等𨋢就睇到！</span> 最快靚正就痴係𨋢入邊，又或者攝係平時啲公告板入邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以痴𨋢門<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>3.痴各交通工具入邊</strong></span><br />\n開始有風險既一個做法，比人捉到會比人鬧，或觸犯唔知乜春例<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以揀d 陰濕位痴<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">例如番工番學準備定一兩張文宣痴好雙面膠，臨落車先痴</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>4.痴文宣上自己身，番工番學做流動宣傳</strong></span><br />\n難，難在恥力不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一般人唔慣痴野上身比人用異目睇，不過為左香港， i do<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以痴係背脊或背囊，冇咁尷尬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>5. 擺街站，派傳單</strong></span><br />\n最難，但都係最有效接觸到唔同類型既人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有安全風險，最好約埋幾個一齊做，揀人流多，未入夜既時間，事半功倍</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇少宣傳，多一個人做，效果雖然唔明顯，但如果多10萬個人做宣傳，個效果就好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家諗到其他方法都可以做，gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊copy 去其他post 比大家睇到"},{"pid":"a929b4ac135a7be85b4eaaecca699dd4a7674b96","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:05:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"59be091bc7467ce410938c3c21806ee8829dba72","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:52:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f21f76b21fc1caf788fe07c49ae4af441e2203a8","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T05:58:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"052d6c3f40d794680e7d1853907087e19cc9aab6","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:34:04.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"0b9fcb2c572ceae6fc1857733a1d859b722eb67a","tid":1593300,"uid":195846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:06:15.000Z","msg":"Tui"}]}